Package: ocom-ocbp-t4201-driver
Version: @VERSION@
Section: text
Priority: optional
Architecture: @ARCH@
Maintainer: OCOM Driver Maintainers <support@example.invalid>
Installed-Size: @INSTALLED_SIZE@
Depends: cups, cups-client, python3, libcups2 | libcups2t64, libcupsimage2 | libcupsimage2t64
Recommends: cups-filters, ghostscript
Description: CUPS driver and ZPL translator for the OCOM OCBP-T4201
 Provides a 203 dpi CUPS raster-to-TSPL2 filter, PPD, host-side
 ZPL-to-TSPL2 translator, 101.6 x 38.1 mm label defaults, automatic USB
 queue configuration, and a ZPL barcode test print.
